<p dir="RTL" style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif'';">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Vazir'',''sans-serif'';">۷- </span></span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Vazir'',''sans-serif'';">احساس مزمن پوچی</span></span></span></span></p>
