<p dir="RTL" style="margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif'';"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Vazir'',''sans-serif'';"><span style="color: red;">ناآگاهی</span></span></span> <span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"><span style="font-family: ''Vazir'',''sans-serif'';"><span style="color: red;">شخصیت نمایشی</span></span></span></span></span></p>
